OL,3,CReport projects dramatic shortage in
OL,4,Chousing for registered workers
OL,6,FA report by Statistics Jersey has
OL,7,Fwarned of a dramatic shortage in
OL,8,Faccommodation for non-qualified
OL,9,Fresidents if current immigration
OL,10,Fpatterns continue.
OL,12,FThe Future Housing Needs report,
OL,13,Fpublished this week, shows shortfalls
OL,14,Fin property supply across several
OL,15,Fcategories, with the biggest issue
OL,16,Fconcerning one-bedroom accommodation.
OL,18,FThe organisation says that its data is
OL,19,Fbased on "the intentions of households
OL,20,Fand projected demographic changes".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
