OL,3,CReport projects dramatic shortage in
OL,4,Chousing for registered workers
OL,6,FLast year, Jersey's net migration was
OL,7,F670 people, an increase of 510 from
OL,8,F2024.
OL,10,FUnder one model forecasting for 2028,
OL,11,Fif 600 more people came to Jersey than
OL,12,Fleft each year, there would be 640 too
OL,13,Ffew one bedroom properties for non-
OL,14,Fqualified residents. Most immigrants
OL,15,Fwho come to the island to work have
OL,16,Fthat status.
OL,18,FThere would also be shortages for
OL,19,Fqualified workers who want to live in
OL,20,Fone or two bedroom accommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
