OL,3,CReport projects dramatic shortage in
OL,4,Chousing for registered workers
OL,6,FWhy does immigration matter?
OL,8,FIn Jersey, immigration matters even
OL,9,Fmore in the housing crisis because of
OL,10,Fthe different types of properties
OL,11,Fsomeone can live in, depending on
OL,12,Ftheir status.
OL,14,FThat means that if more people without
OL,15,Fhousing qualifications arrive in the
OL,16,Fisland, whilst those with them leave,
OL,17,Fthe housing stock becomes increasingly
OL,18,Funbalanced.
OL,20,FWhat are the different types of
OL,21,Fmigration?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
