OL,3,CReport projects dramatic shortage in
OL,4,Chousing for registered workers
OL,6,FAlmost all people who come to the
OL,7,Fisland fall under one of the following
OL,8,Fcategories:
OL,10,FThe most recent immigration figures,
OL,11,Fwhich cover 2024, continued the trend
OL,12,Fof more Entitled people leaving Jersey
OL,13,Fand more Registered people coming to
OL,14,Fthe island to work. That year, 960
OL,15,FRegistered people arrived, whilst 810
OL,16,FEntitled people left.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
