OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783714848
OL,3,CReport projects dramatic shortage in
OL,4,Chousing for registered workers
OL,6,FJersey has the smallest number of
OL,7,FRegistered properties and the largest
OL,8,Fnumber of Entitled homes, with strict
OL,9,Frestrictions on new buildings. That
OL,10,Fmeans the availability deficit is
OL,11,Flikely to continue to grow.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
